# Tests that a graph can be created, three node and
# four edges from different parents to the same child can be added, 
# and one node and four edges can be printed out.

# Create a graph
CreateGraph TheLordOfTheRing

# Add four nodes
AddNode TheLordOfTheRing Frodo
AddNode TheLordOfTheRing Gandalf
AddNode TheLordOfTheRing Samwise

# Add four edges
AddEdge TheLordOfTheRing Gandalf Frodo TheHobbit
AddEdge TheLordOfTheRing Samwise Frodo TheReturnOfTheKing
AddEdge TheLordOfTheRing Samwise Frodo TheTwoTowers
AddEdge TheLordOfTheRing Samwise Frodo TheFellowshipOfTheRing

# Print the nodes in the graph and the outgoing edges from Frodo, Gandalf and Samwise
ListNodes TheLordOfTheRing
ListChildren TheLordOfTheRing Frodo
ListChildren TheLordOfTheRing Gandalf
ListChildren TheLordOfTheRing Samwise